blog.description: A blog that has all the basics for starting your own PMD tabletop campaign!

summary: I wanted to know-- would you ever host an online-based campaign for this? I definitely want to DM this for my friends, but I...
question: I wanted to know-- would you ever host an online-based campaign for this? I definitely want to DM this for my friends, but I feel like I should play it first to get a full understanding.
answer:
Oh! Hello there :D

That is actually a fascinating idea that I wouldn’t be opposed to, I would just have to figure out the logistics of how I’d do it. I think a lot of people use Discord and/or roll20 to run online D&D games, so I know it’s not impossible. My biggest concern is how to get the dungeons to run online.

Do any followers know of any good programs for this? Or if you were a part of an online campaign, how did your DM run it? I would love to do something like this for interested players!
